{"tha-ap171:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap171:0.2":"Suparicariyavagga ","tha-ap171:0.3":"Samadapakattheraapadana ","tha-ap171:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap171:1.2":"mahapugagano ahu; ","tha-ap171:1.3":"Tesaham pavaro asim, ","tha-ap171:1.4":"mama baddhacara ca te. ","tha-ap171:2.1":"Sabbe te sannipatetva, ","tha-ap171:2.2":"punnakamme samadayim; ","tha-ap171:2.3":"Malam kassama sanghassa, ","tha-ap171:2.4":"punnakkhettam anuttaram. ","tha-ap171:3.1":"Sadhuti te patissutva, ","tha-ap171:3.2":"mama chandavasanuga; ","tha-ap171:3.3":"Nitthapetva ca tam malam, ","tha-ap171:3.4":"vipassissa adamhase. ","tha-ap171:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap171:4.2":"yam malamadadim tada; ","tha-ap171:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap171:4.4":"maladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap171:5.1":"Ekunasattatikappe, ","tha-ap171:5.2":"eko asi janadhipo; ","tha-ap171:5.3":"Adeyyo nama namena, ","tha-ap171:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap171:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap171:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap171:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap171:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma samadapako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap171:8.1":"Samadapakattherassapadanam navamam. "}